wikipedia_page.main: Jo Hunter  (born 27 May 1991) is an English field hockey player who plays as a forward for Buckingham and the  England and Great Britain national teams.In 2017 she married England hockey goalkeeper George Pinner.

response: In June 2012 he was one of seven GB hockey athletes to pose for the centerfold of Cosmopolitan magazine as part of a campaign to raise awareness of male cancers and the Everyman cancer charity. In 2017 Pinner married England hockey international Jo Hunter.
